                <h3 class="font-lora font-bold text-[16px] text-logo-dark leading-snug m-0">{item.q}</h3>
                <svg class="cag-faq-chevron flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#e8604c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="cag-faq-panel"><div class="cag-faq-panel-inner"><p class="font-sora text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed px-5 pb-5 m-0" set:html={item.a}></p></div></div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 12. GO DEEPER (cluster routing) -->
    <section class="py-12 px-4 md:py-14">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-clay font-sora text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Go Deeper</p>
        <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-logo-dark mb-4">What Should You Read Next — Whichever Road You Choose?</h2>
        <p class="font-sora text-stone-600 text-[15px] leading-relaxed mx-auto" style="max-width:70ch;">For the numbers, our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-adoption-cost/">adoption cost breakdown</a> handles rescue fees and rehoming math while the <a href="/african-grey-parrot-price/">price guide</a> covers the breeder side. Bringing home a rehomed bird? The <a href="/how-to-tame-african-grey-parrot/">taming guide</a> is your roadmap. Leaning toward a baby? Start with the <a href="/captive-bred-african-grey-parrot/">captive-bred guide</a> and our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-faq/">buyer FAQ</a> — and either way, verify everything against the <a href="/how-to-avoid-african-grey-parrot-scams/">scam-prevention guide</a> before any money moves.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 13. FINAL CTA + CONTACT -->
    <div class="cag-seam" aria-hidden="true"><span class="cag-seam__line"></span><img src="/cag-footer-logo.png" alt="" width="200" height="66" loading="lazy" /><span class="cag-seam__line"></span></div>

    <section class="pt-12 px-4 md:pt-14 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-clay font-sora text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Talk It Through</p>
        <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-logo-dark mb-4">Not Sure Which Road Fits Your Home? Ask Us — We'll Answer Honestly</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px] mx-auto" style="max-width:70ch;">Tell us about your household and what drew you to African Grey adoption, and we will reply within 24 hours with a straight answer — including "an avian rescue sounds like your better fit" when that is the truth. And if a hand-raised, captive-bred baby is the right road, every C.A.Gs Grey comes PCR DNA-sexed, health-screened, vet-certified, and placed with complete CITES Appendix I documentation, shipped nationwide ($185 airport / $350 home).</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div id="contact" class="scroll-mt-20">
